{"tid":1102721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"薄被蓋頭半歲男嬰昏迷　送院不治","createTime":"2019-04-12T02:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T01:39:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":53,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"fc29fe4af18ad05fc1203cbd2439c927d1b07569","tid":1102721,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T02:16:14.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山有BB昏迷。今早(12日)6時35分，沃泰街8號曉峯灣畔3座一單位，一名約6個月大的男嬰昏迷，母親發現大驚報警。男嬰由救護車送院搶救，惜返魂乏術，警方正就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，男嬰為父母的第二胎，他與父母及祖父母同住上址。男嬰父母均要上班，主要由祖父母照顧。昨日(11日)男嬰因身體不適前往睇醫生，至今日凌晨2時許，父母曾經望過男嬰，當時未有異樣。豈料，男嬰今晨在客廳睡覺時，被發現全身冰冷，頭部遭薄被遮蓋昏迷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190412/mobile/bkn-20190412074612375-0412_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190412%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190412074612375-0412_00822_001.html&d=Cuyai%2BbkQ%2BZKjwazMoctzkYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=17953883\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190412/mobile/bkn-20190412074612375-0412_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a20fb21be8f2e2b29e6ee8d5ffbcfb47aa6dc740","tid":1102721,"uid":196924,"like":400,"dislike":21,"score":379,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T02:17:39.000Z","msg":"半歲就放客廳夜晚由佢一個瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n生仔真係要考牌"},{"pid":"f6b09fa2cb3fc8b47d11a2aef65d932219652cf4","tid":1102721,"uid":5178,"like":81,"dislike":3,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"咁樣 會唔會變凶宅?"},{"pid":"f08b728b0b13fd90e09c3ef713476cdf6a9a5ef2","tid":1102721,"uid":157994,"like":245,"dislike":5,"score":240,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T02:19:40.000Z","msg":"點解人類嬰兒咁廢 半歲都會咁死法"},{"pid":"8e037aeb75af7619a3556c37a41f2a39b37532aa","tid":1102721,"uid":21226,"like":109,"dislike":9,"score":100,"quote":{"pid":"f6b09fa2cb3fc8b47d11a2aef65d932219652cf4","tid":1102721,"uid":5178,"like":81,"dislike":3,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T02:17:51.000Z","msg":"咁樣 會唔會變凶宅?"},"citedBy":3,"re